✈️ DELICATE DESIGN; The stylish unique style, noble and elegant design, catering to the new trend of fashion. No matter travelling on the weekends or go abroad, you will be the distinctive one. Suitcase lining made of high quality and safe polyester fabric; PERFECT GIFTS; Beloved, friends, parents, Christmas, saint valentine, birthday, anniversary, mother's day, new year, Thanksgiving etc

✈️ SATISFACTION GUARANTEED; Limited 2 year manufacturer warranty plus trusted companion promise, which covers the cost of repair for damage for any manufacturer defect or replace the defective bag; CASE DIMENSIONS: 21.5 X 10 X 14.5 inch; BAG WEIGHT 3.5 lbs.This item is not intended for use by children 12 and under.
body.description: Betsey Johnson, conquers a dualism between Rock and Roll,This is significant in its overall design philosophy. The designer patterns bring a vacation-ready vibe to this Betsey Johnson suitcase. Each piece is made from a signature fabric. This wheeled duffel use reinforced handle poles for extra strength and durability. The construction of the bag is designed to maximize space and leave extra room for packing when you need it. This is a beautiful piece of traveling art piece specially designed for the environmentally conscious modern lady.The dimensions of the product: 21.5 X 10 X 14.5 inchesThe product has been extensively tested to fit the overhead cabin requirements for most airlinesThe weight of the luggage is approximately 3.4lbThis luggage is covered by a 2 year manufacturer’s warranty.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wheels are durable and balanced
reviews.reviewText: Used it this past week for first time and was very happy with it. Plenty of room for my 4 day trip (even with 3 pairs of shoes inside). Sturdy wheels that stay balanced & never wobbled. Even when I added the extra weight of my purse on top, it stayed balanced. It's a tiny bit over the standard airline guidelines for size, BUT I had no problem at all getting it into either overhead compartment. I am very pleased with it. It does tend to lean forward if you have it fully loaded and sitting upright with the handle extended, but it didn't tip.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very useful and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: I just got back from vacation and used this as my carry on. It was so roomy. For the first time my suitcase was under 50 pounds. I was able to put a packing case in it along with ALL my cosmetics PLUS I still had room. The front pocket was super convenient for keeping my boarding pass and all the travel paperwork I needed. I had so many people ask where I got this from because it was so easy to put the handle down and put it in the overhead bin. This is a definite buy!! Best travel purchase I made! Thank you Betsy Johnson!!!
